Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OBEY THE MONSTERS\N{\i1}As you can see from the pitiful state{\i0}\N{\i1}of the Hero Association{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OBEY THE MONSTERS\N{\i1}humanity has no chance of winning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OBEY THE MONSTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OBEY THE MONSTERS\N{\i1}We must surrender completely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We must surrender completely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,COOPERATE WITH THE MONSTERS\NHUMANITY CANNOT WIN!!\N{\i1}If we resist, it's certain{\i0}\N{\i1}we'll all be slaughtered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,COOPERATE WITH THE MONSTERS\NHUMANITY CANNOT WIN!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,COOPERATE WITH THE MONSTERS\NHUMANITY CANNOT WIN!!\N{\i1}And therefore,{\i0}\N{\i1}the Monster Worship Party has come up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with the only possible solution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER WORSHIP\NOBEY THE MONSTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER WORSHIP\NOBEY THE MONSTERS\N{\i1}By offering human sacrifices{\i0}\N{\i1}regularly to the monsters{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER WORSHIP\NOBEY THE MONSTERS\N{\i1}and controlling{\i0}\N{\i1}their rate of consumption{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER WORSHIP\NOBEY THE MONSTERS\N{\i1}we can avoid the complete extinction{\i0}\N{\i1}of our species.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we can avoid the complete extinction{\i0}\N{\i1}of our species.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those of you who want to side{\i0}\N{\i1}with the monsters, come with us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We must survive in a world where{\i0}\N{\i1}common sense and moral values{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}are being rewritten!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die\Nthan side with the monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER\NVery well!\NYou can be the first sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Offering up sacrifices just\Nto save yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're underestimating monsters\Nway too much, you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm disappointed at how easily{\i0}\N{\i1}human society can be shaken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If things are already like this,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm worried that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when I make my dramatic entrance{\i0}\N{\i1}as the most powerful monster{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it won't make much of an impact.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER TRAITS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.83,0:03:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER TRAITS\N{\i1}In several areas, some citizens{\i0}\N{\i1}have caused outbreaks of violence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MONSTER TRAITS\N{\i1}carrying out robberies, burglaries,{\i0}\N{\i1}and purse-snatchings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}carrying out robberies, burglaries,{\i0}\N{\i1}and purse-snatchings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Police and heroes are working{\i0}\N{\i1}side by side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}patrolling the streets and urging caution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In City S,{\i0}\N{\i1}another group has appeared{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}proclaiming that the end of{\i0}\N{\i1}human history has come{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}spreading confusion as{\i0}\N{\i1}they march through the streets.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just because monsters{\i0}\N{\i1}are on a rampage{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it doesn't mean{\i0}\N{\i1}your own crimes are excused.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monster Association{\i0}\N{\i1}half-asses everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that's why those loudmouthed punks{\i0}\N{\i1}get more brazen...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bumped into me\Nold man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got any complaints?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. He bumped into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.33,0:03:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's drunk and out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters are gonna\Nkill us all anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell should I hold back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're blocking the entrance.\NBeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.93,0:04:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say somethin'?\NYou punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.73,0:04:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not like them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can unleash true terror that{\i0}\N{\i1}will silence even these scumbags.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But right now, I'm too hungry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is your extra-thick steak\Nmega-eater set
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with a super-sized portion of rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a meal fit for a mammoth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't nearly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me everything on this meat menu\Nfrom top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also take every kind\Nof salad you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, and also give me\Na ton of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to order more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CRUNCH CRUNCH\NNOM NOM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CHOMP CHOMP\NMUNCH MUNCH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CRUNCH CRUNCH\NCHOMP CHOMP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CHOMP CHOMP\NMUNCH MUNCH
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GULP GULP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SLAM
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm stuffed.{\i0}\N{\i1}That was a meal fit for a baboon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wallet's gone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I drop it back at the supermarket{\i0}\N{\i1}when I bought napa cabbage?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh...crap.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I could call Genos,{\i0}\N{\i1}but he's broken right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This month's lunch special{\i0}\N{\i1}is fried deep-sea fish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although public safety is a concern{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}our restaurant maintains{\i0}\N{\i1}strict security measures{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}against robbery, violence,{\i0}\N{\i1}and dine-and-dash incidents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A former pro hero is also stationed{\i0}\N{\i1}in our security office.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you can dine without worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.23,0:06:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn... After hearing that announcement,{\i0}\N{\i1}if I tell a waiter about my situation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it'll just look like I got scared{\i0}\N{\i1}and turned myself in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh crap, what a mess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the biggest crisis{\i0}\N{\i1}I've faced all year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be the end for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm talking to you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saitama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not what it looks like!\NI was just...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I looked all over\Nfor you, Saitama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.97,0:06:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left in the middle\Nof our conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're looking for\Nthe Hero Hunter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then.\NI'll help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'd like to add to my order.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- In return, I'm taking...\N- One extra large fries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...70% of the points as a success fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've quickly risen to\NClass B, Rank 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be hard to climb\Nhigher from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this goes well, reaching top five\Nof Class B is definitely possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for that,\Nyou'll need my cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably\Ndon't even know anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about your target or\Ntheir facial features, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, you're hopeless.\NI'll provide you with the intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE\NFrom now on, you will follow\Nmy instructions and act accordingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE\NYou listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAZE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fries, sir. Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sharing with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with that grin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must be thrilled to{\i0}\N{\i1}be working with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe Saitama will now join{\i0}\N{\i1}the Blizzard Bunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dine-and-dasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't done it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone catch that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dine and dashing is a terrible crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- I'll go after him.\N- Hey... Saitama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate a fry, right?\NThe bill's on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One...fry?{\i0}\N{\i1}Are you kidding me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world's falling apart and{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he's being this petty?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.16,0:08:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess a marathon was still\Na bit too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better to heal your wounds
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under the protection of\Nthe Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, you'll need to\Nfulfill a condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bring back a hero's head," huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you kill a hero,\Nyou're officially considered a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of logic is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters should be able to incite\Nabsolute fear with their mere presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, my head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.78,0:09:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tareo, how did you get out alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're a monster too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, an ugly monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww, that hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.38,0:09:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mommy!\N- Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that ugly cry-face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder they bully you.\NPoor kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are the odds\Nwe meet twice on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old dude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me, old. I'm only 18!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SNAP\NDon't call me, old. I'm only 18!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me, old. I'm only 18!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and go home.\NThe sun's going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters might come out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For running away earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heroes were trying to kill you,\Nbut that was a mistake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you protected me from\Nthe bullets that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just now. You saved me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're a champion of justice and—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out.\NYou're giving me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dine-and-dasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dine-and-dasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.24,0:10:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scumbag!\NHow dare you leave without paying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your timing was perfect, you scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll let it slide this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so let this be your warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come to fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared now?\NWhat's your hero name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cape...Caped Baldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? I didn't catch that.{\i0}\N{\i1}But he does look like a hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He may be a small fry,{\i0}\N{\i1}but I'll hunt any hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even in the Hero Almanac,\Nso I bet he's new.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old dude... Did you dine and dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'll let it go,\Nso don't hassle him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a joke.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I start getting pity{\i0}\N{\i1}from the Monster Association{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and even from small-time heroes and brats,{\i0}\N{\i1}then I'm really done for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When I heard that{\i0}\N{\i1}the old geezer survived, I felt relieved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It makes me sick to think{\i0}\N{\i1}that I felt that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever the definition of a monster is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's clear I don't have{\i0}\N{\i1}the resolve to be one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If a hero's head is what you want,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'll get you one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.82,0:11:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't underestimate me...{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm a monster.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm just as guilty as you,\Nso I can't be seen with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to knock him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh great, a witness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's that book?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of all people, it had{\i0}\N{\i1}to be some hero-obsessed kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess my cover's blown.{\i0}\N{\i1}Damn it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kid, do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HERO ALMANAC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HERO ALMANAC\NLet me take a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HERO ALMANAC
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even listed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Figures...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who was that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Punch Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Punch Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, old dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bald hero guy said, "I screwed up"\Nand ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost...?!\NW-What kind of hero was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he hit your head in a bad spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garou, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been watching you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like us, Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.\NIt's a shame but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lack the qualities of\Na true monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey kid...\NStop staring and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys wanna have a word with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in my almanac.\NIt wasn't just hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is he doing...here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,URBAN LEGEND MONSTER\NKING THE RIPPER\NW-What is he doing...here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,URBAN LEGEND MONSTER\NKING THE RIPPER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's King the Ripper.\NHe's abducted many kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's King the Ripperrrr!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying and get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you had such\Na small friend, Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop! Talk from over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to make you cry yet.\NMy bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to savor\Nthose screams later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to chop up\Nevery last inch of your body to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're doomed. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.90,0:15:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.03,0:15:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to be interrupted\Nwhen I'm meditating. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you send King the Ripper\Nand Insect God?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was just for observation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't need to send\Nthose two brutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? They may actually\Nget along surprisingly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two never follow orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably get carried away\Nand kill Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially King the Ripper.\NHe's a rare breed that kills for pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the other monsters\Nwon't go near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, that was my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let them make contact with Garou
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that it would stimulate him\Nand promote his growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Growth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a trial for that indecisive boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we need to\Ntear apart his body and his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until they are in tatters...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to seeing\Nhow he changes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after experiencing monsters firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyoro-Gyoro, what are you after?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you really intend\Nto do with Garou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.67,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason. Just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.88,0:16:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Phoenix Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you think\NLord Orochi came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he an ancient creature\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Orochi was once human like Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After countless failures and sacrifices,\Nhe finally became the ultimate lifeform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is truly worthy of\Nthe name, Monster King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was I who created Lord Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Created? You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Garou is trained properly,\Nhe might become a second Lord Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only I know the secret to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.79,0:17:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've instructed Insect God to intervene
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if King the Ripper goes too far\Nwith Garou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if he dies,\Nthen that's just how it goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just wait for the next\Nsuitable specimen to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I scoped out the area and{\i0}\N{\i1}sealed the back entrance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the last few hours,{\i0}\N{\i1}no one has come or gone but the gorilla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other members are all out.{\i0}\N{\i1}This is the perfect time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The command center is{\i0}\N{\i1}probably located inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.61,0:17:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps in the monitor room.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A strange group of unidentified people{\i0}\N{\i1}recently moved in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've been bringing in{\i0}\N{\i1}large amounts of equipment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and mysterious powders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.33,0:17:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And boxes filled with putrid matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The information I've gathered{\i0}\N{\i1}matches my suspicions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No doubt about it.{\i0}\N{\i1}It must be them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now's the time. I'm going in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyoro-Gyoro ordered us to\Nobserve your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.18,0:18:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To determine if you're truly worthy\Nof joining our ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero Hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you just some freak who gets off\Non pretending to be a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.08,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you a true monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Look at you,\Ntalking all high and mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just getting sick of\Nhow soft you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then. Kill that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster is one who has\Nabandoned being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A being severed from\Nthe world of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you help that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is unacceptable.\NYou must kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to join\Nthe Monster Association
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must work hard to gain our trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you haven't fully let go\Nof being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:19:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any half-hearted types.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're building\Nan organization that will
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,destroy human society\Nand take control.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We kill kids off like their nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.25,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just now, you even lost\Nto that mediocre hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were caught off guard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt how useful you'd be in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I already told you.\NHurry up and go home, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs are shaking...\NI can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think someone will help you\Nbecause you can't stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's gonna help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In moments like this,\Nthe only choice is to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You need to get strong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up! Tareo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.74,0:20:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our enemy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself the Hero Hunter,\Nyet you haven't killed a single soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like I thought,\Nyou're a spineless wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last... I've finally tracked them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My archenemies I've hunted for years,\Nthe ones most entwined with my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The worst organization in history\Nthat's plotting to wipe out humanity
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and reshape the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had started to suspect\Ntheir true identity from recent events.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I could never get a solid lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibabawa prophesized\Nthat the Earth is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pulling the strings behind\Nthe so-called Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the true masterminds\Nbehind it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HOUSE OF TAKOYAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.49,0:23:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The House of Evolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A customer?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a customer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You keep relocating your base
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this time, your front is\Na takoyaki stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.83,0:23:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know your little schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.80,0:23:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're still getting ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am now a hero called Zombieman.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.93,0:23:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one with a body that can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Experimental Sample\NNo. 66 rings a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're a hero who's come to\Ntake down the House of Evolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.02,0:23:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but the House of Evolution\Nhas already been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...you want to come inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.83,0:23:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got some free time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:24:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ORGANISM LIMITS

